==English==

=== Etymology ===
From Irish, ''sean'', old, and ''tigh'', a house.

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ænti|-ænti]]

===Noun===
'''Shanty'''
#An old run-down house or shack.  
#Sailors' work song.
